commit.message:
Use 1hr TTL for system/tools cache breakpoints, add change logging

- System[-1] and tools[-1] now use {"type": "ephemeral", "ttl": "1h"}
- Messages[-2]/[-3] stay at 5m default {"type": "ephemeral"}
- Log tool_result reordering and cache_control changes only when
  the proxy actually modified the request

